import Layout from "../../components/ui/Layout";
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';

const Preferences = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Layout>
                <Form>
      <Form.Check // prettier-ignore
        type="switch"
        id="custom-switch"
        label="Check this switch"
      />
      <Form.Check // prettier-ignore
        disabled
        type="switch"
        label="disabled switch"
        id="disabled-custom-switch"
      />
                </Form>
            </Layout>
        </>
    )
}
export default Preferences;
